            "title": "兒子豪擲1.3億買Pokémon卡　SkyBridge創辦人：他極有投資眼光",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">投資公司 SkyBridge Capital創辦人Anthony Scaramucci之子AJ Scaramucci，似乎承襲父親的投資基因，年輕的 AJ 被他的對沖基金大亨父親形容為「對收藏品投資極具眼光的創投人士」，他本月成功競得網紅Logan Paul珍藏的寶可夢（Pokémon）卡。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"兒子AJ Scaramucci（左）豪擲1.3億買Pokémon卡，SkyBridge創辦人Anthony Scaramucci：他極有投資眼光。資料圖片。 (Photo by Roy Rochlin/Getty Images for Anthony Scaramucci )\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"719\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/dtgPY32h4RMlh72gdWxVBw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTcxOQ--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-02/57be2910-1369-11f1-b7f7-298728feef60\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">兒子AJ Scaramucci（左）豪擲1.3億買Pokémon卡，SkyBridge創辦人Anthony Scaramucci：他極有投資眼光。資料圖片。 (Photo by Roy Rochlin/Getty Images for Anthony Scaramucci )</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link rapid-with-clickid etailiffa-link athena-button\" data-i13n=\"sec:shop-now;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Yahoo;elmt:other;pdid:\" data-ylk=\"slk:下載Yahoo財經APP;sec:shop-now;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Yahoo;elmt:other;pdid:;itc:0\" href=\"https://mobile.yahoo.com/finance?pid=editorial&amp;c=HK_Acquisition_YMktg_Evergreen_[%E2%80%A6]ub2=HK_YMktg&amp;af_sub4=1058&amp;af_sub5=article__Banner_&amp;uuid=s1kW4IOA4iZoKC480912&amp;uuid=n71xwVw3nRy25ecw0845&amp;uuid=cSM0RfGjBMAB6hoF0568&amp;uuid=DuIuMOWACtzsBO9v0182&amp;uuid=xB4uJWWz1ECOpprK0310&amp;uuid=tI3bFLm2SkvtQBBV0990&amp;uuid=fxfksXClqFqTK6wd0763&amp;uuid=ybkNYokd68f51swq0786&amp;uuid=FMZsYcaovPDiRiEn0238&amp;uuid=DBJmJP7M8dIuFAza1268&amp;uuid=UfT13nXCr4cvW6En0657&amp;uuid=PXZAVgzDtTubfzB50492&amp;uuid=vKvKMdPxcax8uKVB0858&amp;uuid=b9lwBa9QJpW1nDGE0691&amp;uuid=vlRWlWNhKBZhiAgc0737&amp;uuid=uYLODeNHhsonQhC20339&amp;uuid=pifNpXs63jptqi5H0279&amp;uuid=qp3YUzwMSdJD6vlL0645&amp;uuid=rSYcc3skG3GLP5390333&amp;uuid=1R5wK6mBCx7lpBL30982&amp;uuid=uv2JhhemlLAEcqZS0245&amp;uuid=HPOVGtqDrX1VPYoP0134&amp;uuid=Vbm9qeF23UbKFUwV0740&amp;uuid=Vo0ggtFtaaFjlbAR0293&amp;uuid=Ahrs29aW8UxKfVmp0319&amp;uuid=KY0FM5IlGv5VyL3b0194&amp;uuid=soNUUI0W39s6NWaQ0319&amp;uuid=fF9FZQ3iPNdsnDWO0733&amp;uuid=NOj3FXU9Tx70uoXQ0820&amp;uuid=MhCeryurfIarguZ70925&amp;uuid=dJI9g1zfikEQ3MMB0696&amp;uuid=MoePYhrruAkd1rRs0006&amp;uuid=3uloGdI2IxSVhxco0690&amp;uuid=0g1fhWirY5eHWOo00348&amp;uuid=pB3zJNo2pNKJnGDT0310&amp;uuid=5uff9nLVdntja92R0991&amp;uuid=lVoURqEo4b225m8c0686&amp;uuid=r1VKOeN31MjW7xI90753&amp;uuid=q0kOLvuspTV2UEMx0255&amp;uuid=Lz5GIZHDJSDguZTU0988&amp;uuid=8KB2pkDP7CtTJEfn0031&amp;uuid=e0jKA61WpqkKrpy20289&amp;uuid=M5Bw1vIAZqmSrjxV0292&amp;uuid=SLaEgDglJvf5GRMv0638&amp;uuid=d7EEH4xTRhgNOlXW0638\">下載Yahoo財經APP</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>美股外幣即時報價 多國新聞任睇</strong></p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\"><strong>1.3億買卡 </strong>媒體曝光價值<strong>15.6億</strong></h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這張全球唯一、獲PSA 10最高評級的卡牌，成交價約1,650萬美元（約1.3億港元），為Logan Paul於2021年購入價格的三倍以上。該拍賣歷時41天，共吸引97名競投者，於2月16日結束。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-e36a98f1-d494-40eb-98f8-0bbd44bc1db7-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Scaramucci在Yahoo Finance節目《Opening Bid Unfiltered》最新一集表示：「我當然和他是共同投資人﹐他正管理我們家族部分資金，也創辦了一家名為Treasuretrove.com的公司。」他指出，這張卡牌帶來的市場關注，有助AJ在迅速擴張的收藏品市場站穩陣腳。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Scaramucci表示：「人們需要明白，這張1,650萬美元卡牌的購買，帶來約2億美元（約15.6億港元）的媒體曝光價值⋯⋯我們其中一個策略，是藉此幫助AJ在收藏品領域打響名堂，讓大家知道他將成為一股不可忽視的力量，隨着他展開這場尋寶之旅。」</p><div class=\"flex flex-col items-center\"><blockquote class=\"flex flex-col items-center mb-module-gap twitter-tweet\"><div class=\"card-loader shadow-card-loader relative box-border overflow-hidden bg-[#ffffff] mb-[10px] h-[200px] max-w-[500px] rounded-[2px] p-[10px] before:bg-dirty-seagull before:shadow-card-loader-before before:block before:h-[110px] after:absolute after:top-0 after:left-0 after:h-full after:w-full after:bg-linear-[to_right,rgba(255,255,255,0)_0,rgba(255,255,255,.6)_30%,rgba(255,255,255,0)_81%] after:animate-[card-loader-animate_0.6s_linear_infinite] w-full\"></div><p class=\"break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Let's get this into the Nintendo Museum in Kyoto and cement it as the \"Mona Lisa\" of the Pokémon Franchise. <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:@Nintendo;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://twitter.com/Nintendo?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">@Nintendo</a> <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:@Pokemon;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://twitter.com/Pokemon?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">@Pokemon</a> <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:@Museum_Nintendo;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://twitter.com/Museum_Nintendo?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">@Museum_Nintendo</a> <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:pic.twitter.com/SPe56Jo6PB;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://t.co/SPe56Jo6PB\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">pic.twitter.com/SPe56Jo6PB</a></p><p class=\"break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">— AJ Scaramucci (@jedimooch) <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:February 17, 2026;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://twitter.com/jedimooch/status/2023888485401457021?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">February 17, 2026</a></p></blockquote></div><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\"><strong>押注貨幣貶值與流動性錯配</strong></h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">他補充：「如果你相信貨幣貶值，而我們家族確實如此，那麼這是一個存在流動性錯配的新前沿；比特幣（<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:BTC-USD;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/BTC-USD/\">BTC-USD</a>）與黃金已相當成熟，但收藏品價格上升是有原因的。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">根據Grand View Research資料，美國收藏品市場規模於2025年估值為321.3億美元，預計到2033年將達480.8億美元，2026年至2033年間年均複合增長率為5.3%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推動增長的因素包括年輕收藏家參與度提升、數碼及轉售市場擴展、鑑定與評級標準改善、懷舊文化類別影響力上升，以及收藏品被更廣泛視為與傳統資產並列的另類價值儲存工具。</p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\"><strong>「文化遇上商業」推動需求</strong></h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">StockX共同創辦人兼Ghostwrite創辦人Josh Luber在同一節目中表示，收藏品市場強勢的關鍵在於供需，他表示：「這本質上就是供求關係。當文化遇上商業時，需求便會啟動。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Luber等合著的白皮書《The Blindboxification of Everything》指出，商業遊戲化已成為全球第二具顛覆性的經濟力量。這不僅關乎球鞋與卡牌，而是產品如何捕捉文化潮流的演變，例如Paul那張保存完好的寶可夢卡，如今已屬於AJ Scaramucci。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Scaramucci總結道：「如果你買的是頂級優質藏品，我認為它具有持久性，能長期保值。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>撰文：Brian Sozzi（Yahoo Finance執行編輯）<br/>原文：</strong><a class=\"link yahoo-link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:2;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:Anthony Scaramucci on son buying Logan Paul’s $16.5 million Pokémon card: He’s going to be a force;cpos:2;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas;outcm:mb_qualified_link;_E:mb_qualified_link;ct:story;\" href=\"https://finance.yahoo.com/news/anthony-scaramucci-on-son-buying-logan-pauls-165-million-pokemon-card-hes-going-to-be-a-force-133149939.html\"><strong>Anthony Scaramucci on son buying Logan Paul’s $16.5 million Pokémon card: He’s going to be a force</strong></a></p></div>",
