            "title": "美股日誌｜ 納指回落　Nvidia業績靚仔仍跌 5%",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"美股日誌｜ 納指回落 Nvidia業績靚仔仍跌 5%\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"595\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/9sDYo24BMawQ..gWzxHwrw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU5NQ--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-02/b727d2d0-135e-11f1-95fe-ec5392f3553b\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">美股日誌｜ 納指回落 Nvidia業績靚仔仍跌 5%</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國股市周四自早段更大跌幅中回穩，但整體仍告下跌。納數下跌1.2%；標普500指數下跌約0.6%；傳統股為主的道指則微升。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:Nvidia;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/NVDA/\">Nvidia</a>儘管上個財季利潤近翻倍勝預期，數據中心業務收入續增75%，仍未能令投資者驚喜，華爾街對人工智能的回報潛力及顛覆風險憂慮升溫。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Nvidia股價下跌逾 5%。儘管該晶片巨頭季度收入及盈利均大幅超越預期，並上調業績指引，但投資者反應平淡。集團對未來展望的推動因素缺乏細節，且未計及潛在的中國市場收入，令部分華爾街人士質疑其競爭壓力及人工智能建設需求的持續性。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-000db8c5-51f7-4275-b668-a7731c36c44e-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:2;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:下載Yahoo財經APP;cpos:2;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"